thread.title: Clarence

author: Clarence
title: Clarence
text:
Your price was good, but performances (5 colored cartridges) for my Epson Artisan 730, NOT GOOD.
I replaced my empty Epson cartridges w/ you products, and they worked for one day. Yes, just one day. Then, came this message on the printer (Epson Artisan 730) screen: "Cannot recognize the following cartridge(s) 99/98".
As suggested, I removed and re-installed them--three times. No luck.
Any suggestions?
CBina
Bismarck
